title: American Horror Story Weekly Wednesday Live Stream #34
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Thank you for always being here with new AHS news and info. I still believe that you deserve to be a writer on American Horror Story because your theories are always awesome and are things that could possibly play into some story beats coming up. Never stop being awesome, Mary!

epic superhero theme song playing I AM PATREON 🤜🤛
Thank you for everything you do, Mary! Also mega thanks to Tami, Casey, Maisie & the rest of your support team that bring us fans together and put up with our shenanigans. ;) #StayFreakyMyFriends
Thanks for making me feel so appreciated as a viewer!❤
Sorry I missed the stream. I was asleep. But I'm looking forward to this season. I'm so excited. Under 2 weeks away.
